# UI Patterns

## Dashboard (Alpine.js v3)
- HTML is exported as template literal strings from TypeScript files
- Uses Alpine.js v3 from CDN — always use component function pattern:
```javascript
// Correct (v3)
x-data="myComponent()"
function myComponent() { return { prop: '', method() { ... } }; }

// WRONG (v2 — will break)
document.querySelector('[x-data]').__x.$data
```
- Tailwind CSS loaded from CDN (`cdn.tailwindcss.com`)
- Dashboard state managed in `app()` function in `dashboard.ts`
- API calls go through `this.api(method, path, body)` helper

## Customer Pages
- `customerPageHtml` — full BestSecret-style loyalty page
- `widgetHtml` — compact embeddable iframe widget
- Both fetch from `/c/:slug/api/me?email=X&token=Y`
- Use vanilla JS (no framework) for customer-facing pages
- Widget sends `postMessage({ type: 'loyalty-resize', height })` for iframe auto-resize
